Class ShareCodeMappingTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • me.timothy.tests.database.ShareCodeMappingTest
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    MysqlShareCodeMappingTest

    public class ShareCodeMappingTest
extends java.lang.Object
    Describes a test focused on testing a ShareCodeMapping inside a MappingDatabase. The database must be cleared prior to each test. The database will be modified in each test. Do not run against a production database.
